snippet.title: Overwatch 2: Fight the Invasion Trailer | The Null Sector Threat
snippet.description:
The Invasion begins.

As Null Sector descends upon cities across the globe, the Overwatch Task Force prepares to fight the oncoming threat. Will our Heroes’ efforts be enough to save Future Earth or will they fold in the face of their powerful new enemies? 

An all-new adventure begins in Overwatch 2: Invasion, launching Aug 10 at 12pm PT!
_
